{"type":null,"faqId":18038,"title":"荣耀3C 4G版 Emui3.0短信发送失败异常？","answer":"<p>原因分析：<br>\n短信发送失败的原因有很多，请逐一排除：<br>\nA：是否可以拨打电话，排除您卡欠费的情况；<br>\nB：检查短信中心设置是否正确，短信中心不正确会导致短信发送失败。（信息--&gt;菜单--&gt;设置--&gt;高级--&gt;短信中心--&gt;检查值是否正确）<br>\n具体短信中心号码请咨询对应移动服务运营商。<br>\nC：检查是否运营商禁止您发送短信，请拨打运营商客服电话；<br>\nD：换一张正常的卡，测试是否可以正常发送，排查您卡的问题。特别是您第一次使用这张卡的时候。<br>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"808","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420446291000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":95,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀3C,4G版,EMUI3.0,3.0,信息,发送,异常","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}